headline: NFP Appoints Yuna Nordeen to U.S. Growth Leader Role Within Construction and Infrastructure Group
summary: NFP, an Aon company and leading property and casualty (P&C) broker, benefits consultant, wealth manager and retirement plan advisor, has appointed Yuna Nordeen as senior vice president, U.S. growth leader, Construction and Infrastructure (C&I). Nordeen, who is based in Chicago, will report to Adrian Pellen, managing director and co-leader of NFP's C&I Group.
